12", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75608434_3888160121466645_4102924857382221306_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EDpCPS7tp-UQ7kNvgElc3Hr&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Af2YBbuWh0Eu8Nvn2Eefvd-&oh=00_AYAv8rjfXiMQmfS_0jw-rZ80964QzRcRLozv-6z2Sh4XXg&oe=66EAAABC"}, {"file_name": "38974771_914663160423989_8412528913888708301_n.png", "id": "1471442040147115", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003240_1471442043480448_4137664387287025678_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=SQEDPw8-uTEQ7kNvgG3KKpK&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Af2YBbuWh0Eu8Nvn2Eefvd-&oh=00_AYD35Imjk1iAUjZEztVCIyoypo4yR9-hPj4IxSFTJsmtmA&oe=66EAAF16"}, {"file_name": "57568678_442736708598857_2601426099645306453_n.png", "id": "1585260168698302", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57569443_1585260175364968_5377620633503669556_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YbIojCVxFMIQ7kNvgE9tma3&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Af2YBbuWh0Eu8Nvn2Eefvd-&oh=00_AYDdJa2lUpFBPdyiqFz96PzzQrrAYhIgcyaSkqrFieODZg&oe=66EAA1F8"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Simtryx", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Experience the next step in virtual simulations for healthcare**\n\nTalk, observe, and interact with your patient to diagnose them correctly inside the most immersive and accessible simulation for VR headsets.\n\nImmerse yourself with our powerful main features:\n\n- **AI-powered speech simulation**: Talk freely with the patient to learn more about their history, habits, and to empathize with them.\n- **Advanced hand tracking**: Built from the ground up with hand tracking in mind, every object in the world has a physical presence, and your virtual hands won't phase through.\n- **Seamless onboarding**: Through video passthrough, bring 3D elements into your physical space and jump into the simulation in the most comfortable way.\n\nWith our focus on accessibility, ease 